From 80893e91bde3c686a031bdc749a086001385afa4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tarang <tarangjammalamadaka9@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 12 Apr 2026 14:49:25 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] feat: real analytics, PDF export, dashboard insights, UI
 polish

- Analytics page computes all metrics from real Supabase jobs
- Export page: working PDF report with jspdf (summary, status, companies, sources)
- Dashboard: InsightsCards (weekly activity, response rate, pipeline days, top source)
- Sidebar: grouped nav sections with headers
- Landing page: gradient hero, 8 feature cards, sticky nav
- App shell: gradient background, max-width container
- Pipeline stats: refined pill colours

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
